{{DiseaseDisorder infobox
| Name        = 偏執狂<br>Paranoia
| ICD10       = F20.0, F22.0, F22.8
| ICD9        = {{ICD9|295.3}}, {{ICD9|297.1}}, {{ICD9|297.2}}
